        "title": "fix: read Windsurf Devin session from app origin",
        "body": "## Summary\n- read structured Windsurf/Devin localStorage from `https://app.devin.ai` before the legacy `https://windsurf.com` origin\n- keep `app.devin.ai` and `windsurf.com` values isolated as separate complete session candidates so partial new-origin data cannot poison a legacy fallback bundle\n- add importer and fetch-path regression coverage for partial app-origin storage plus complete legacy-origin storage\n\n## Verification\n- `./Scripts/lint.sh lint`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `swift test --filter 'WindsurfWebFetcherTests|WindsurfDevinSessionImporterTests' --skip-update` was attempted twice on head `e8aecd9f`; both local runs stopped before compilation because SwiftPM stalled downloading the Sparkle 2.9.1 binary artifact. CI should provide the full Swift test/build signal.\n\nFixes steipete/CodexBar#1564",
